  "description": "OXBOW coupling. Dark baritone voice with OXBOW's knot topology creating labyrinthine reverb paths. The entangled reverb wraps around the low partials, creating standing waves that reinforce different harmonics depending on the pitch played. Every key reveals a different room in the same infinite building. Portamento enabled for architectural glides between spaces.",
